You will need...

The main executable GForm (on git main page)

The gambas3 runtime installed
sudo apt-get install -y gambas3-runtime

Download the example scripts to see usage like how to use the pipes for comunuication between the GUI and the script.
Download the text help files for instructions.

Or download the complete package
Download the GForm_dist.zip for the GForm Application, sample scripts,snapshots and help files.

Download the GForm_source.zip for just the gambas basic source code

Happy scripting :)
